column5: hey folks. this listing is available for ten more minutes.  i'm not a river fisherman, but those of you who are..thought you would get a good deal. it is 2:42 at time of posting.  they are patagonia wading shoes. i have no idea if they are good. if you get this later, then check back at this site from time to time as they do tend to repeat the listing a few times.  http://www.steepandcheap.com/  i've ordered other stuff from them and found them very reliable.
